These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-3-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, fanta, soy-milk
There 4 different types of food: cherry, peas, pepper, spinach
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, hiking, magic-tricks, puzzles
House: palace, townhouse, victorian, cape-cod
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, bellflower, lily, orchid
4 different games are played: chess, canasta, backgammon, poker
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, helicopter, snowmobile
 1. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 2. the person playing backgammon is the person eating spinach##1
 3. the person eating peas is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person playing canasta##1
 5. the palace house is on the right of the victorian house##1
 6. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
 7. the townhouse house is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
 9. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person eating peas##3
11. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
12. the person drinking 7up is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person eating spinach##2
13. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
14. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who growslily##1
15. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person eating cherry##3
16. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left or far right##3
17. the palace house is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Beverage    | soy-milk   | 7up            | almond-milk | fanta        |
| Food        | peas       | pepper         | spinach     | cherry       |
| Hobby       | hiking     | drawing        | puzzles     | magic-tricks |
| House         | townhouse     | cape-cod | victorian    | palace   |
| Flower         | lily    | orchid         | zinnia        | bellflower         |
| Game       | poker    | chess       | backgammon    | canasta     |
| Transport   | helicopter | snowmobile     | car         | bike         |

