.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-3-2::.
City: london, marseilles, paris, new-york
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, grapes, peach, raspberry
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, blood-red, amber, new-yorkcher
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, disaster, thriller
4 different games are played: snooker, chess, billiard, canasta
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hedgehog, lizard, snake
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, ice-hockey, skateboarding, swimming
 1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
 2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person who's sport is swimming and the owner of the hedgehog##2
 3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is the person eating raspberry##1
 5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
 8. the person who likes new-yorkcher is the person eating peach##1
 9. the person eating grapes is between the person playing billiard and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
10. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
11. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
13. the person traveling to paris is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
14. the person eating eggplant is on the far right##1
15. the person playing chess is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
16. the person watching thriller movies is the person playing snooker##1
17. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| City      | new-york           | marseilles   | london      | paris     |
| Food          | peach         | grapes     | raspberry  | eggplant |
