 7. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the wooden house##1
 8. the cottage house is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
 9. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the palace house##3
10. the person eating pumpkin is on the far right##1
11. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is the havana-smoker##1
13. the palace house is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
14. the person who's hobby is singing is the cottage house##1
15. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
16. the person watching musical movies is the person who's birthday is in november##1
17. the person watching drama movies is the person who's birthday is in july##1
18. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person eating lemon##1

