There 4 different types of food: lemon, blueberry, kiwi, lettuce
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, sailing, skateboarding, soccer
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, june, november, may
 1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 2. the art-deco house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in june is the person drinking lemonade##1
 4. the coach is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 6. the cape-cod house is the person eating lettuce##1
 7. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
 8. the fisherman is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 9. the person who's sport is sailing is the fan of punk##1
10. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
11. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the fisherman##1
12. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
13. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
14. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
15. the fan of blues is between the fan of punk and the person who's sport is soccer##2
16. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
17. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
18. the art-deco house is the person drinking 7up##1
